widgets.label: %key

widgets.onValue: set("BubbleReverbMixMeter", (value * 100))

if (value === 0) {
  set("BubbleReverbColorMeter", "1970s")
  set("BubbleReverbColorDescription", "1970s: downsampled (10KHz bandwidth), dark, noisier modulation")
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbValhallaID", "reverbIDColor1", "#f28018") 
  setVar("BubbleReverbReverbID", "reverbIDColor1", "#f28018") 
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbVintageID", "reverbIDColor2", "#b11323")  
  
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbDecayPanel", "reverbColor1", "#f28018")    
  setVar("BubbleReverbColor", "reverbColor1", "#f28018")  
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbDecay", "reverbColor6", "#ffffff")

  setVar("BubbleReverbModPanel", "reverbColor2", "#b11323")   
  setVar("BubbleReverbRate", "reverbColor2", "#b11323")  
  setVar("BubbleReverbDepth", "reverbColor2", "#b11323")  
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbMixPanel", "reverbColor3", "#ea431c")   
  setVar("BubbleReverbMix", "reverbColor3", "#ea431c")   
  setVar("BubbleReverbPredelay", "reverbColor3", "#ea431c")   
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbDampingPanel", "reverbColor4", "#f8a12f") 
  setVar("BubbleReverbHighFreq", "reverbColor4", "#f8a12f") 
  setVar("BubbleReverbHighShelf", "reverbColor4", "#f8a12f") 
  setVar("BubbleReverbXover", "reverbColor4", "#f8a12f") 
  setVar("BubbleReverbBassMulti", "reverbColor4", "#f8a12f") 
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbEqPanel", "reverbColor5", "#890002")
  setVar("BubbleReverbHighCut", "reverbColor5", "#890002")   
  setVar("BubbleReverbLowCut", "reverbColor5", "#890002")   
}

else if (value === 0.5) {
  set("BubbleReverbColorMeter", "1980s")
  set("BubbleReverbColorDescription", "1980s: no downsampling (full bandwidth), dark, noisier modulation")
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbValhallaID", "reverbIDColor1", "#ffffff")  
  setVar("BubbleReverbReverbID", "reverbIDColor1", "#ffffff")  
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbVintageID", "reverbIDColor2", "#8b16ff")  
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbDecayPanel", "reverbColor1", "#8b16ff")    
  setVar("BubbleReverbColor", "reverbColor1", "#8b16ff")  
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbDecay", "reverbColor6", "#ffffff")

  setVar("BubbleReverbModPanel", "reverbColor2", "#b11323")   
  setVar("BubbleReverbRate", "reverbColor2", "#b11323")  
  setVar("BubbleReverbDepth", "reverbColor2", "#b11323")  
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbMixPanel", "reverbColor3", "#4f65ff")   
  setVar("BubbleReverbMix", "reverbColor3", "#4f65ff")   
  setVar("BubbleReverbPredelay", "reverbColor3", "#4f65ff") 
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbDampingPanel", "reverbColor4", "#8e15ff") 
  setVar("BubbleReverbHighFreq", "reverbColor4", "#8e15ff") 
  setVar("BubbleReverbHighShelf", "reverbColor4", "#8e15ff") 
  setVar("BubbleReverbXover", "reverbColor4", "#8e15ff") 
  setVar("BubbleReverbBassMulti", "reverbColor4", "#8e15ff") 
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbEqPanel", "reverbColor5", "#890002")
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbDecay", "reverbColor6", "#ffffff")
}

else if (value === 1) {
  set("BubbleReverbColorMeter", "NOW")
  set("BubbleReverbColorDescription", "NOW: no downsampling (full bandwidth), bright, clean modulation")
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbValhallaID", "reverbIDColor1", "#f28018")  
  setVar("BubbleReverbReverbID", "reverbIDColor1", "#f28018")  
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbVintageID", "reverbIDColor2", "#b11323")  
  
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbDecayPanel", "reverbColor1", "#f28018")    

  setVar("BubbleReverbModPanel", "reverbColor2", "#b11323")    
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbMixPanel", "reverbColor3", "#ea431c")   
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbDampingPanel", "reverbColor4", "#f8a12f") 
  setVar("BubbleReverbHighFreq", "reverbColor4", "#8b16ff") 
  setVar("BubbleReverbHighShelf", "reverbColor4", "#8b16ff") 
  setVar("BubbleReverbXover", "reverbColor4", "#8b16ff") 
  setVar("BubbleReverbBassMulti", "reverbColor4", "#8b16ff") 
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbEqPanel", "reverbColor5", "#890002")
  
  setVar("BubbleReverbDecay", "reverbColor6", "#ffffff")
}
set("BubbleReverbHighShelfMeter", (24 * (value - 1)))
set("BubbleReverbSizeMeter", (value * 100))
set("BubbleReverbAttackMeter", (value * 100))
set("BubbleReverbDiffMeter", (value * 100))
set("BubbleReverbLateMeter", (value * 100))
set("BubbleReverbDepthMeter", (value * 100))
set("BubblePhaseSpeedMeter", (value * 100))
set("BubblePhaseInMeter", (48 * (value - 0.5)))
set("BubblePhaseOutMeter", (48 * (value - 0.5)))
set("BubblePhaseMixMeter", (value * 100))
